com.i2group.apollo.alertingapi

Interface IAlertDispatcher


  • public interface IAlertDispatcher
    A dispatcher that sends Intelligence Analysis Platform alerts using custom delivery mechanisms.

    • Method Summary

      Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      void dispatchAlert(String subscriberName, Collection<IAlertDeliveryMechanism> destinations, IAlert alert)
      Dispatches the specified IAlert to the user with the specified name, using the specified IAlertDeliveryMechanisms.

    • Method Detail

      • dispatchAlert

        void dispatchAlert(String subscriberName,
                 Collection<IAlertDeliveryMechanism> destinations,
                 IAlert alert)
        Dispatches the specified IAlert to the user with the specified name, using the specified IAlertDeliveryMechanisms. The value of IAlertDeliveryMechanism.getTypeId() determines whether an IAlert should be dispatched by this IAlertDispatcher.
        Parameters:
        subscriberName - A String containing the name of the subscribing user.
        destinations - The IAlertDeliveryMechanisms that should be used to deliver the IAlert.
        alert - The IAlert to be dispatched.
